---
title: "withdraw (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_access: onlyRole(DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE)
    q_access --> q_validateTo: to == address(0)
    q_validateTo --> q_revert: to is zero
    q_validateTo --> q_iter: to is non-zero
    q_revert --> [*]: revert Errors.InvalidZeroAddress()
    q_iter --> q_transfer: i < assetAmounts.length
    q_iter --> q_final: i >= assetAmounts.length
    q_transfer --> q_iter: safeTransfer(to, assetAmounts[i].amount); i++
    q_final --> [*]

    note right of q_iter
        INV-001: all assets transferred to same destination address
        INV-002: loop iterates over all provided asset-amount pairs
    end note
